The spiral is the usual “Ulam’’ spiral  

\[
\begin{array}{ccc}
5&4&3\\[-2pt]
6&1&2\\[-2pt]
7&8&9
\end{array}
\]

with \(1\) at \((0,0)\), \(2\) at \((1,0)\) and so on.  

For a point \((x,y)\) let  

\[
k=\max(|x|,|y|) .
\]

All numbers with the same \(k\) lie on the same “ring”.  
The smallest number on ring \(k\) is  

\[
S_k=(2k-1)^2+1 ,
\]

situated at \((k,\,-(k-1))\).  
Going upward on the right edge increases the number by one each step.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### Position of 2026  

\(2026\) is the first number of ring \(k=23\) because  

\[
(2\cdot 22+1)^2 =45^2=2025 <2026\le 47^2=(2\cdot23+1)^2 .
\]

Thus \(2026\) is at  

\[
(23,\,-22).
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### The eight neighbours

The eight neighbour coordinates are  

\[
\begin{aligned}
&(22,-23),\;(23,-23),\;(24,-23),\\
&(22,-22),\;(24,-22),\\
&(22,-21),\;(23,-21),\;(24,-21).
\end{aligned}
\]

We evaluate the number on each of them.

*Ring \(k=23\) (bottom edge)*  

Bottom‑left corner of this ring is \((-23,-23)\) with number  

\[
2163=S_{23}+6\cdot23-1=2026+137.
\]

Moving right, the number increases by one. Hence  

\[
\begin{aligned}
(22,-23)&: 2163+(22+23)=2208,\\
(23,-23)&: 2209\;(=47^2).
\end{aligned}
\]

*Ring \(k=22\) (inner corner)*  

\[
(22,-22)= (2\cdot22+1)^2=45^2=2025 .
\]

*Ring \(k=22\) (right‑edge start)*  

\[
(22,-21)=S_{22}= (2\cdot22-1)^2+1 =43^2+1 =1850 .
\]

*Ring \(k=23\) (right edge, one step up)*  

\[
(23,-21)=S_{23}+1 =2026+1 =2027 .
\]

*Ring \(k=24\) (right edge of the next outer ring)*  

The start of ring \(24\) is  

\[
S_{24}=(2\cdot24-1)^2+1=47^2+1=2210
\]

at \((24,-23)\).  
Moving upward on the right edge adds one per step:

\[
\begin{aligned}
(24,-23)&=2210,\\
(24,-22)&=2211,\\
(24,-21)&=2212 .
\end{aligned}
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### Sum of the neighbours

\[
\begin{aligned}
\text{Sum}&=2208+2209+2210+2025+2211+1850+2027+2212\\
&=11050+2025+2027+1850\\
&=11050+4052+1850\\
&=16952.
\end{aligned}
\]

\[
\boxed{16952}
\]
----
